descripcion: The top ten pilots travel to the 2018 DRL Allianz World Championship. They battle it out in a five-man semifinal in on the most vertical course of the season, over and past three high-rises. Temperatures rise in the Finals, as the pilots battle it out in the most important seven heats of their lives to crown the DRL 2018 World Champion.
